Template: gamemode/add_user_to_group
Type: note
Description: Gamemode User Group Configuration
 To enable all features of 'gamemode', add the user to the 'gamemode' group.
 .
 You can add a user to the 'gamemode' group with the following command:
 .
 sudo usermod -aG gamemode <username>
 .
 After adding the user to the group, you will need to log out and back in for the changes to take effect.
 .
 Make 'gamemode' enabled by default using
 .
 systemctl --user enable --now gamemoded
Description-zh_CN.UTF-8: Gamemode 用户组配置要求
 要启用‘gamemode’的所有功能，需将用户添加到‘gamemode’用户组。
 .
 您可以使用以下命令将用户添加到’gamemode‘用户组：
 .
 sudo usermod -aG gamemode <username>
 .
 添加用户到组，您需要注销并重新登录以使更改生效。
 .
 设置：
 .
 systemctl --user enable --now gamemoded
 .
 使得’gamemode‘默认启动。
